### Articles API quick tests

@base = http://localhost:5000/api

### List first page
GET {{base}}/articles?page=1&limit=5

### Meta counts
GET {{base}}/articles/meta

### Create
POST {{base}}/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hello News",
  "summary": "Short summary",
  "content": "<p>Body</p>",
  "category": "Breaking",
  "language": "en",
  "status": "draft",
  "tags": ["demo","test"]
}

### Get by slug/id (replace :id)
GET {{base}}/articles/:id

### Update (replace :id)
PUT {{base}}/articles/:id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "published"
}

### Archive (replace :id)
PATCH {{base}}/articles/:id/archive

### Restore (replace :id)
PATCH {{base}}/articles/:id/restore

### Delete (soft) (replace :id)
DELETE {{base}}/articles/:id
